{"tid":1321941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想寫返完整嘅歷史紀錄，記錄由六月九日起發生嘅事件","createTime":"2019-07-15T20:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:02:47.000Z","uid":40855,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13c22eb75f5258b03d53f585d60179527765eb73","tid":1321941,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:59:35.000Z","msg":"主要係以市民角度敘述事件，記低每次行動嘅前因後果，輿論/網上意見，用更立體嘅角度去睇返件事。<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講係一本歷史書，相似嘅例子有記錄八九民運嘅《人民不會忘記》，無論最後贏定輸，份嘢都可以畀後世較為容易了解事情始末，甚至作為日後官方調查報告嘅參考資料。<br />\n<br />\n誠招幫手，唔一定要文筆好，初步覺得最主要係資料滙集梳理，目錄未有，可以加我tg再傾。<br />\n<br />\n記住，大家都係旁觀者，入咗群你都唔好同人講你幾時做過啲乜，無人有興趣知。<br />\n<br />\n太多限制真係上唔到前線，但我相信任何位置都可以出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hk_independent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk_independent&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=5fa463ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hk_independent</a>"},{"pid":"15ef291b179c7b9481538746cfe24e337fbd2572","tid":1321941,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T21:00:29.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djqmRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djqmRS</a>"},{"pid":"d309440dd8ada366e8c1b76263b30677f4b73a62","tid":1321941,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T21:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b0725e66771650880c1467df9dbf7337df3f65d","tid":1321941,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5be61c7ee6536db3b343ab66a8baf46372fff6b7","tid":1321941,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a3e9dfe4524a7448f19d19526437a4cdf124877","tid":1321941,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa7148ea4d085f2